📌 Project Overview

The Beauty Blog Website is a modern and responsive blogging platform designed to share:

🌿 Skincare routines
💄 Makeup tips
🧴 Natural beauty remedies

This project demonstrates a professional frontend structure, combining clean UI design with smooth animations and responsive layout.

✨ Key Features

✔ Organic Skincare Blog
✔ Lip Care Tips Article
✔ Natural Face Mask Guide
✔ 🌙 Dark Mode Toggle
✔ 📱 Fully Responsive Design
✔ 🖼 Image Hover Animations
✔ 🔗 Related Posts Section
✔ ✨ Scroll Animations (AOS Library)

