⚙️ Installation Guide
1️⃣ Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/beauty-blog.git
cd beauty-blog
2️⃣ Run Project

Simply open:

index.html

or use Live Server (VS Code).

🚀 Deployment

You can deploy this project on:

Netlify
Vercel
GitHub Pages
Steps:
Push project to GitHub
Connect repo to Netlify / Vercel
Deploy instantly
